<html><DIV>::FireBlade::</DIV>
<DIV>FireBlade reaches the access to outside and leaves out it to wait for Megatron and the rest to start with Megatron's plans.  He just sits there without moving. Slowly the metal of his body starts to blend in all of his surroundings. It is almost impossible to tell him from the background. He moves his hand and his metal converts back to it's original flame red color. 'Everything seems to be working the same as before I was exiled'. "Where are they?" he asks himself. </DIV><br clear=all><hr>Get Your Private, Free E-mail from MSN Hotmail at <a href="http://www.hotmail.com">http://www.hotmail.com</a>.<br></p></html>
